ic%2C%20I'll%20be%20careful%20here%2C%20it%20can%20mimic%20things%20that%20are%20sent%20to%20it%20that%20it%20detects%2C%20turn%20it%20around%20and%20send%20it%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20becomes%20a%20hole.%20A%20black%20hole.%20It%20becomes%20mostly%20undetectable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20634-pound%20pod%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Reaper%20Defense%20Electronic%20Support%20System%2FScalable%20Open%20Architecture%20Reconnaissance%20(RDESS%2FSOAR)%2C%20will%20allow%20the%20Reaper%20drone%20%26quot%3Bto%20somewhat%20disappear%20off%20of%20enemy%20radar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20first%20tested%20the%20pod%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20by%20General%20Atomics%20and%20L3Harris%20Technologies%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20from%20the%20time%20describes%20the%20pod%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20broad%20spectrum%2C%20passive%20Electronic%20Support%20Measure%20(ESM)%20payload%20designed%20to%20collect%20and%20geo-locate%20signals%20of%20interest%20from%20standoff%20ranges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20that%20its%20addition%20to%20the%20Reaper%20helps%20it%20become%20%26quot%3Ban%20even%20more%20versatile%20surveillance%20aircraft%20given%20its%20ability%20to%20conduct%20electronic%20sensing%20well%20enough%20to%20provide%20high%20quality%20intelligence%20but%20also%20keep%20safely%20away%20in%20friendly%20or%20international%20airspace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20from%20Smith%20come%20off%20the%20back%20of%20the%20US%20Navy's%20intense%20battle%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthis-getting-smarter-red-sea-attacks-ships-paying-the-price-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20around%20the%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2036-foot-long%20Reaper%20struggled%20somewhat%20against%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fyemen-houthi-