venia%20and%20the%20US.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20stereotypical%20American.%20I'd%20never%20left%20the%20US%20until%20I%20moved%20to%20Slovenia%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20passport%20until%20I%20was%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Tennessee.%20I%20lived%20near%20Nashville%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20two%20children%20until%20we%20moved%20to%20Monterey%2C%20California%2C%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e069c366-b7ab-4c87-8c3e-80f42e0ea8b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20never%20heard%20of%20Slovenia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20an%20adventurous%20side.%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20world%20beyond%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20military%2C%20came%20home%20and%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20moving%20to%20Slovenia%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20Slovenia%20was%20a%20country.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20he%20meant%20Slovakia.%20Even%20though%20Slovenia%20is%20between%20Italy%20and%20Croatia%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-trips-to-book-for-2024-underrated-destinations-travel-planner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewasn't%20popular%20with%20American%20tourists%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20to%20Ljubljana%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20with%20our%20two-%20and%20three-year-old%20sons%20in%20December%202016.%20I%20had%20a%20sheltered%20upbringing%20in%20a%20small%20town.%20When%20we%20first%20arrived%2C%20I%20was%20immediately%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20English%20people%20spoke.%20I%20thought%20people%20would%20only%20speak%20Slovene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20many%20people%20speak%20English%20in%20European%20countries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20own%20language.%20It%20was%20mind-blowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22604cfa5