t%20helped%20him%20learn%20boundaries%20in%20a%20safe%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20learned%20how%20to%20ride%20a%20bike%20there.%20I%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20cycling%20on%20roads%20with%20him%20than%20I%20would%20have%20in%20the%20US%20because%20I%20trusted%20the%20drivers%20to%20look%20out%20for%20cyclists%20and%20pedestrians.%20They're%20more%20used%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20let%20him%20take%20his%20bike%20to%20a%20skate%20park%20and%20ride%20down%20a%20barrel.%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20let%20him%20do%20that%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20seeing%20other%20parents%20allow%20it%20gave%20me%20more%20confidence%20and%20pushed%20me%20as%20a%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20had%20more%20freedom%20to%20explore%20the%20city%20without%20worrying%20about%20cars%2C%20and%20they%20became%20much%20more%20confident%20and%20independent%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283004957-81d6-4cc5-ba0c-d8c0177c65ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreschool%20was%20cheaper%20and%20there%20was%20less%20focus%20on%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20my%20kids%20went%20to%20preschool%20in%20Ljubljana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20preschool%20was%20focused%20on%20security.%20When%20I%20first%20went%20to%20visit%20my%20kids'%20preschool%20in%20Slovenia%2C%20I%20accidentally%20wandered%20through%20the%20kitchen%20instead%20of%20the%20admin%20office.%20It%20was%20no%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wouldn't%20happen%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20more%20security%20checks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-pulled-kid-out-of-school-because-active-shooter-drills-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20good%20reason%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20in%20Slovenia%20people%20were%20less%20concerned%20about%20needing%20security%20in%20daycares%20and%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20parents%20to%20pay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%