2title%22%3A%22Menstrual%20Leave%20Petition%20In%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Flags%20A%20Flip%20Side%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMandating%20menstrual%20leave%20for%20women%20may%20lead%20to%20them%20being%20shunned%20from%20the%20workforce%20and%20go%20against%20them%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20for%20courts%20to%20look%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20that%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20to%20frame%20policies%20for%20menstrual%20leave%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMandating%20such%20leaves%20will%20lead%20to%20women%20being%20shunned%20from%20workforce.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20that%20what%20we%20try%20to%20do%20to%20protect%20women%20can%20act%20to%20their%20disadvantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20actually%20a%20government%20policy%20aspect%20and%20not%20for%20the%20courts%20to%20look%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20relates%20to%20multiple%20policy%20aspects%20and%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20the%20court%20to%20intervene.%20%26quot%3BWe%20permit%20the%20petitioner%20to%20move%20the%20secretary%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20and%20to%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati.%20We%20request%20the%20secretary%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20at%20the%20policy%20level%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20after%20consulting%20all%20stakeholders%20and%20see%20if%20a%20model%20policy%20can%20be%20framed%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20this%20ruling%20will%20not%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20any%20state%20government%20taking%20steps%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20taken%20a%20similar%20stand%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20when%20a%20petition%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20all%20states%20to%20frame%20rules%20for%20menstrual%20pain%20leave%20for%20women%20students%20and%20employees.%20Back%20then%2C%20too%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20the%20matter%20falls%20in%20the%20policy%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Kerala%20are%20the%20only%20two%20states%20in%20the%20country%20that%20have%20a%20provision%20for%20menstrual%20leave.%20While%20Bihar%20has%20a%20two-day%20leave%20policy%20for%20women%20employees%2C%20Kerala%20has%20a%20provision%20for%20a%20three-day%20period%20leave%20for%20women%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720426980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdbuvihn_supreme-court-istock_625x300_02_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-supreme-court-menstrual-leave-will-lead-to-women-being-shunned-top-court-flags-period-leave-flip-side-6058694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mandating%20menstrual%20leave%20for%20women%20may%20lead%20to%20them%20being%20shunned%20from%20the%20workforce%20and%20go%20against%20them%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20for%20courts%20to%20look%20into.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-supreme-court-menstrual-leave-will-lead-to-women-being-shunned-top-court-flags-period-leave-flip-side-6058694%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-supreme-court-menstrual-leave-will-lead-to-women-being-shunned-top-court-flags-period-leave-flip-side-6058694%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdy-chandrachud-supreme-court-menstrual-leave-will-lead-to-women-being-shunned-top-court-flags-period-leave-flip-side-6058694%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Killer%20brat'%20absconding%3A%20Where%20is%20Mumbai%