20neither%20our%20jobs%20nor%20our%20social%20(marital)%20status.%20We%2C%20the%20long%20train%20of%20kids%2C%20competing%20for%20Baba's%20attention%2C%20would%20often%20joke%20about%20much%20later%20in%20life%20how%20our%20bosses%20and%20spouses%20wondered%20about%20our%20sense%20of%20righteousness%E2%80%94something%20that%20fuelled%20the%20tendency%20to%20live%20life%20on%20our%20terms%E2%80%94free%20of%20fear%20or%20favour.%20Baba%20addressed%20the%20next-door%20tea%20hawker%20in%20our%20small%20town%20with%20his%20full%20name.%20He%20addressed%20men%20he%20asked%20for%20directions%20from%20as%20%E2%80%9CShriman%E2%80%9D.%20He%20made%20everyone%20feel%20like%20they%20mattered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoison-sprayed-at-hathras-event-led-to-stampede-claims-godmans-lawyer-6055897%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Poison%20Sprayed%20At%20Hathras%20Event%20Led%20To%20Stampede%2C%20Claims%20Godman's%20Lawyer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%2C%20Baba%2C%20was%20a%20man%20that%20everyone%20needs%20in%20their%20life.%20Someone%20who%20makes%20them%20believe%20in%20the%20justness%20of%20cosmic%20logic.%20Someone%20who%20sees%20and%20hears%20them.%20Someone%20who%20can%20make%20the%20wrongs%20right.%20And%20this%20need%20is%20precisely%20what%20people%20like%20Baba%20Narayan%20Hari%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Saakar%20Vishwa%20Hari%20'Bhole%20Baba'%2C%20prey%20on.%20The%20reason%20I%20have%20jostled%20with%20my%20rational%20mind%20to%20expose%20an%20utterly%20private%2C%20raw%2C%20memory%20for%20all%20and%20sundry%20to%20prey%20on%20is%20because%20I%20can%20only%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20Hathras%20tragedy%E2%80%94a%20stampede%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Esatsang%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20has%20already%20claimed%20at%20least%20121%20lives%E2%80%94through%20decoding%20this%20need.%20It%20doesn't%20help%20my%20rational%20mind%20that%20the%20geographical%20region%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20horrible%20tragedy%20is%20barely%20half%20an%20hour%20from%20where%20I%20was%20born.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20deceased%20was%20known%20to%20my%20family.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mahatma%20And%20A%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20many%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ebabas%3C%2Fem%3E'%20were%20known%20to%20my%20Baba.%20At%20least%20in%20their%20non-%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Elives.%20I%20have%20a%20vague%20memory%20of%20a%20man%20who%20took%20care%20of%20me%20as%20a%20child%20but%20became%20a%20%E2%80%98mahatma'%20later.%20No%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20Gandhian%20about%20this%20Mahatma.%20A%20murder%20investigation%20led%20to%20this%20transformation.%20The%20man%20just%20disappeared%20one%20day.%20When%20he%20emerged%20again%2C%20it%20was%20with%20all%20the%20ritualistic%20bells%20and%20whistles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20another%20memory%20to%20tap%20into%20at%20this%20moment.%20I%20once%20participated%20in%20a%20dance%20competition%20and%20won%20the%20second%20prize%20(I'll%20kill%20to%20win%20a%20dance%20award%20today).%20The%20song%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAaj%20phir%20jeene%20ki%20tamanna%20hai%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20from%20Dev%20Anand-starrer%20%3Cem%3EGuide%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20film%20delineates%20the%20trajectory%20of%20a%20charlatan%2C%20Raju%20%E2%80%98Guide'%2C%20becoming%20a%20self-sacrificing%20godman.%20Raju%20Guide%20didn't%20sign%20up%20for%20being%20a%20holy%20man%2C%20a%20performer%20of%20miracles.%20He%20was%20destined%20to%20be%20so.%20In%20his%20beginning%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Esadhu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20his%20end.%20Unlike%20real%20life%2C%20though%2C%20the%20film%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20poetic%20justice.%20Raju%20Guide%20had%20to%20die%20because%20of%20his%20devotees'%20belief%20in%20his%20superpowers.%20In%20reality%2C%20it%20is%20the%20believers%20who%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-hathras-tragedy-grieving-families-left-with-questions-and-anger-6039208%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0After%20Losing%20Wife%20And%20Son%20In%20Stampede%2C%20Man%20Has%20A%20Question%20For%20'Bhole%20Baba'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20claiming%20to%20have%20direct%20access%20to%20god%E2%80%94of%20whichever%20kind%E2%80%94are%20nothing%20new%20or%20peculiar.%20The%20claim%20of%20divinity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%2C%20most%20effective%20tricks%20to%20avert%20reproach%20and%20responsibility.%20It%20is%20common%20to%20all%20civilisations.%20Nobody%20questions%20those%20who%20claim%20to%20be%20doing%20god's%20work.%20Those%20who%20dare%20meet%20their%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGod%20Is%20Perfect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20in%20India%20claim%20ourselves%20to%20be%20the%20guru%20of%20all%20civilisations%2C%20a%20quick%20note%20on%20how%20our%20belief%20business%20goes.%20Unlike%20the%20Greco-Roman%20gods%2C%20who%20are%20seen%20as%20fickle-minded%20and%20driven%20by%20similar%20passions%20that%20govern%20the%20mortals%2C%20our%20gods%20are%20largely%20seen%20as%20just%20and%20benevolent.%20They%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%20By%20extension%2C%20then%2C%20their%20%E2%80%98conduits'%20or%20representatives%20are%20also%20seen%20as%20doing%20the%20right%20things.%20No%20matter%20how%20wrong%20they%20are.%20Questioning%20them%20becomes%20questioning%20a%20just%20god.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20westward%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20mythology%20opens%20with%20demigods%E2%80%9D%2C%20writes%20Ralph%20Waldo%20Emerson%20in%20%3Cem%3ERepresentative%20Men%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20the%20mythology%20of%20our%20times%2C%20godmen%20are%20the%20demigods%2C%20the%20superhumans.%20In%20etymology%20and%20conceptualisation%2C%20these%20alleged%20superhumans%20come%20from%20Goethe's%20%E2%80%9C%C3%BCbermenschen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nietzsche's%20%E2%80%9C%C3%BCbermensch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shaw's%20%E2%80%9Csuperman%2C%E2%80%9D%20etc.%20Godmen%20see%20and%20thus%20elevate%20the%20unseen%20and%20the%20marginalised.%20They%20also%20see%20and%20alleviate%20the%20fears%20of%20the%20seen%20and%20the%20mainstreamed.%20They%20signify%20hope.%20In%20the%20modern%20mythologies%2C%20this%20is%20the%20role%20of%20comic%20book%20superheroes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhole-baba-hathras-stampede-puts-spotlight-on-indias-craze-for-godmen-6052042%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Hathras%20Stampede%20Puts%20Spotlight%20On%20India's%20Craze%20For%20Godmen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3BSupes%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20his%20assumption%20as%20the%20new%20Superman%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20actor%20Henry%20Cavill%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20a%20rich%20mythology%20and%20they're%20both%20(Superman%20and%20the%20heroes%20of%20Hindu%20mythology)%20rooted%20in%20the%20same%20thing%20-%20hope%20and%20goodness%E2%80%9D.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20very%20hope%20and%20goodness%20of%20Indian%20spiritual%20traditions%20has%20been%20long%20exploited%20by%20charlatans%20pretending%20to%20be%20superheroes.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20these%20sundry%20%3Cem%3Ebabas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ematas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20closer%20to%20what%20the%20OTT%20series%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Boys%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20conceptualised%3A%20the%20%E2%80%9CSupes%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Supes%20have%20superpowers%2C%20they%20have%20infiltrated%20all%20the%20structures%20of%20power%2C%20they%20control%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20and%20they%20are%20self-serving.%20Their%20days%2C%20the%20series%20tends%20to%20suggest%2C%20however%2C%20are%20numbered.%20What%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebabas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ENishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C