t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifteen%20minutes%20later%20Mr%20Rawat%20was%20administered%20a%20second%20oath%20-%20as%20a%20Cabinet%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20double%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20has%20led%20to%20questions%20about%20procedural%20lapses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oath%20ceremony%20faux%20pas%20underlined%20the%20odd%20nature%20of%20Mr%20Rawat's%20induction.%20He%20is%20now%20the%20first%20person%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20a%20BJP%20government%20while%20still%20being%20a%20Congress%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%3F%20Because%20Mr%20Rawat%20has%20not%20yet%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20for%20whom%20he%20was%20also%20Working%20President%20of%20the%20party's%20state%20unit%20and%20the%20MLA%20from%20the%20Vijaypur%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20a%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rawat%20is%20also%20in%20the%20unprecedented%20position%20of%20being%20both%20a%20MoS%20and%20Cabinet%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20because%20he%20did%20not%20formally%20resign%20from%20the%20former%20(after%20being%20administered%20the%20incorrect%20oath)%20before%20taking%20oath%20for%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rawat%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20after%20the%20chaotic%20sequence%20of%20events%20and%20expressed%20gratitude%20towards%20the%20BJP%20for%20making%20him%20a%20minister.%20He%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20his%20not-yet-former%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20no%20right%20to%20accuse%20me...%20there%20is%20no%20resentment%20(from%20my%20side)%20but%20what%20they%20did%20not%20give%20me%2C%20this%20government%20respected%20me...%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20unusual%20oath%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20missed%20the%20word%20'ka'%20by%20mistake.%20I%20took%20oath%20twice...%20I%20am%20the%20first%20minister%20to%20take%20oath%20twice%20in%20half%20an%20hour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20-%20which%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20with%20Speaker%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20-%20to%20disqualify%20Mr%20Rawat%20and%20Nirmala%20Sapre%2C%20another%20now%20ex-leader%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20-%20has%20been%20quick%20to%20react.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Avaneesh%20Bundela%20has%20questioned%20the%20BJP's%20claim%20of%20good%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20government%20of%20Dr%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20be%20about%20good%20governance%2C%20today%20there%20was%20such%20negligence...%20a%20mistake%20like%20this%20has%20probably%20never%20been%20seen%20before%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20there%20is%20confusion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20claiming%20the%20error%20had%20been%20triggered%20either%20by%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Governor's%20office%20or%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20from%20higher%20political%20figures%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20and%20ex-Union%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rawat%2C%20a%20six-time%20MLA%20from%20Sheopur%20district%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20April%2C%20He%20was%20previously%20the%20junior%20Home%20Minister%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Digvijaya%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20induction%20today%20means%20the%20state%20government%20has%2019%20Cabinet%20Ministers%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rawat's%20jump%20to%20the%20BJP%20will%20trigger%20a%20by-election%20for%20his%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720424520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjd6t9sbg_ramniwas-rawat-oath-taking_625x300_08_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-minister-ramniwas-rawat-oath-taking-mla-becomes-minister-twice-in-15-minutes-in-bizarre-oath-taking-ceremony-6058510%22%2C%22summary%22%3