0800296_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwhatsapp-soon-you-could-send-images-to-meta-ai-for-questions-and-edits-124070800296_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20Agrees%20To%20Plead%20Guilty%20To%20Fraud%20In%20Probe%20Into%20737%20MAX%20Crashes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBoeing%20said%20Monday%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20over%20two%20fatal%20737%20MAX%20crashes%2C%20which%20court%20papers%20show%20would%20see%20the%20aviation%20giant%20plead%20guilty%20to%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20comes%20after%20prosecutors%20concluded%20Boeing%20flouted%20an%20earlier%20settlement%20addressing%20the%20disasters%2C%20in%20which%20346%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Ethiopia%20and%20Indonesia%20more%20than%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reached%20an%20agreement%20in%20principle%20on%20terms%20of%20a%20resolution%20with%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20memorialization%20and%20approval%20of%20specific%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20Boeing%20told%20AFP%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20papers%20filed%20in%20Texas%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20company%20had%20agreed%20to%20plead%20guilty%20to%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20to%20defraud%20the%20United%20States%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20certification%20of%20MAX%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20will%20be%20fined%20under%20the%20deal%20and%20must%20invest%20a%20minimum%20of%20%24455%20million%20in%20%26quot%3Bcompliance%20and%20safety%20programs%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20compensation%20for%20families%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing's%20latest%20legal%20predicament%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20DoJ%20determination%20in%20mid-May%20that%20the%20company%20ignored%20a%202021%20deferred%20prosecution%20agreement%20(DPA)%20by%20not%20meeting%20requirements%20to%20improve%20its%20compliance%20and%20ethics%20program%20after%20the%20MAX%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamilies%20of%20MAX%20victims%20were%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20disappointed%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20deal%20reached%20between%20Boeing%20and%20the%20DoJ%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Clifford%20Law%20representing%20them%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuch%20more%20evidence%20has%20been%20presented%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%20that%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20culture%20of%20Boeing%20putting%20profits%20over%20safety%20hasn't%20changed.%20This%20plea%20agreement%20only%20furthers%20that%20skewed%20corporate%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20partner%20Robert%20A.%20Clifford%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20will%20ask%20the%20court%20to%20reject%20the%20plea%20deal%20at%20an%20upcoming%20hearing%2C%20according%20to%20an%20opposition%20filed%20by%20their%20legal%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20DPA%20was%20announced%20in%20January%202021%2C%20over%20charges%20that%20Boeing%20knowingly%20defrauded%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20during%20the%20certification%20of%20the%20MAX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20required%20Boeing%20to%20pay%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20fines%20and%20restitution%20in%20exchange%20for%20immunity%20from%20criminal%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-year%20probationary%20period%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20this%20year.%20But%20in%20January%2C%20Boeing%20was%20plunged%20back%20into%20crisis%20mode%20when%20a%20737%20MAX%20flown%20by%20Alaska%20Airlines%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20after%20a%20fuselage%20panel%20blew%20out%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20May%2014%20letter%20to%20the%20US%20court%2C%20DoJ%20officials%20said%20that%20Boeing%20breached%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20DPA%20by%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20design%2C%20implement%2C%20and%20enforce%20a%20compliance%20and%20ethics%20program%20to%20prevent%20and%20detect%20violations%20of%20the%20US%20fraud%20laws%20throughout%20its%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720421340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fl5q13kco_alaska-airlines-boeing-737-max-9-afp_625x300_25_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-agrees-to-plead-guilty-to-fraud-in-probe-into-737-max-crashes-6058278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing%20said%20Monday%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20over%20two%20fatal%20737%20MAX%20crashes%2C%20which%20court%20papers%20show%20would%20see%20the%20aviation%20giant%20plead%20guilty%20to%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-agrees-to-plead-guilty-to-fraud-in-probe-into-737-max-crashes-6058278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-agrees-to-plead-guilty-to-fraud-in-probe-into-737-max-crashes-6058278%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-agrees-to-plead-guilty-to-fraud-in-probe-into-737-max-crashes-6058278%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hollywood%20icon%20Paramount%20agrees%20%2428bn%20merger%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720421220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6f47%2Flive%2Faf006890-3ced-11ef-bfbc-e3f0644de067.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4ng95d737do%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20studio%20has%20made%20many%20hit%20films%2C%20including%20the%20Godfather%2C%20Star%20Trek%2C%20and%20Mission%3A%20Impossible%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A90%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%