oter.%20The%20crash%20left%20Kaveri%20Nakhawa%20dead%20and%20her%20husband%20Pradeep%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%2C%20Mihir's%20father%20and%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district%2C%20and%20his%20driver%20Rajrushi%20Bidavat%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20today.%20The%20two%20were%20arrested%20last%20evening%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crash%20that%20took%20place%20early%20yesterday.%20Rajesh%20Shah%20was%20arrested%20after%20he%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20the%20cops%20in%20their%20investigation%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lookout%20circular%20has%20been%20issued%20against%20Mihir%20Shah.%20When%20police%20reached%20his%20home%2C%20they%20found%20it%20locked.%20The%20whereabouts%20of%20his%20mother%20and%20sister%20are%20not%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20investigation%20so%20far%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20drank%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20late%20Saturday%20night%20and%20his%20driver%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20high-end%20BMW%20car.%20At%20Worli%2C%20he%20insisted%20that%20he%20would%20drive%20and%20took%20the%20wheel.%20The%20Nakhawas%2C%20Koliwada%20residents%20who%20sold%20fish%20for%20a%20living%2C%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%20from%20Sassoon%20Dock%20when%20the%20BMW%20crashed%20into%20their%20scooter.%20Kaveri%20Nakhawa%20was%20run%20over%20and%20dragged%20by%20the%20BMW%20as%20it%20fled%20the%20scene.%20She%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20doctors%20declared%20her%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20had%20called%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20accident.%20His%20phone%20has%20been%20off%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20new%20criminal%20code%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20rash%20driving%20and%20destruction%20of%20evi