Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flindsey-graham-all-presidential-candidates-should-take-cognitive-tests-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20'Bal%20Buddhi'%20Re-Plug%20On%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Movement%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20on%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20led%20by%20BJP%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20doubling%20down%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bchildish%20mind%26quot%3B%20jab%20at%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20veteran%20and%20Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20described%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20%26quot%3Bbal%20buddhi%26quot%3B%20(childish)%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20%26quot%3Bspreading%20confusion%20and%20lies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20childish%20person%20who%20has%20not%20matured%20yet.%20He%20has%20not%20yet%20become%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20properly.%20He%20says%20we%20(INDIA%20bloc)%20defeated%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement.%20Rahul%20ji%2C%20Ram%20is%20our%20existence%2C%20our%20ideal%2C%20our%20life%2C%20our%20God%2C%20and%20Ram%20is%20the%20identity%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20movement%20has%20thrown%20the%20Congress%20out%20of%20power%20many%20times%20and%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20divine%20and%20grand%20temple%2C%20but%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20only%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Gandhi%20of%20lying%20in%20Parliament%20about%20Agniveer%20martyrs%20and%20the%20government%20of%20not%20providing%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Rahul)%20knows%20nothing%20else%20other%20than%20lying%20and%20spreading%20confusion.%20That%20is%20why%20this%20'Bal%20Buddhi'%20person%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20keeps%20saying%20anything%20that%20comes%20to%20his%20mind.%20No%20one%20understands%20how%20he%20was%20able%20to%20defeat%20the%20(Ram%20Mandir)%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20saying%20whatever%20comes%20to%20mind%20has%20become%20the%20tendency%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Under%20his%20(Rahul%20Gandhi)%20leadership%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20invite%20only%20misfortune%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20been%20infantilising%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20saying%20he%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bchildish%20mind%26quot%3B%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bbalak%20buddhi%26quot%3B%20jab%20at%20the%20Congress%20MP%2C%20now%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20in%20question%20were%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20leader%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20was%20speaking%20about%20the%20Faizabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20--%20of%20which%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20part%20--%20by%20Congress%20ally%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20defeating%20the%20BJP%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20defeated%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement%20that%20was%20launched%20by%20the%20BJP%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani.%20What%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20something%20very%20big...%20Congress%20party%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20defeated%20them%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rath%20Yatra%20was%20launched%20by%20Mr%20Advani%20to%20shore%20up%20support%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%20in%20Ayodhya%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%20The%20yatra%20was%20taken%20out%20in%201990%20and%20multiple%20communal%20clashes%20were%20reported%20along%20its%20route.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20the%2016th%20century%20Babri%20Masjid%20located%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20site%20was%20demolished%20by%20Hindu%20activists%20who%20believed%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20an%20ancient%20temple%20to%20mark%20Ram's%20birthplace.%20Nearly%20three%20decades%20later%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20playing%20up%20the%20Ram%20temple%20construction%20in%20its%20election%20campaign%2C%20the%20Faizabad%20election%20was%20keenly%20watched%2C%20and%20the%20BJP's%20defeat%20there%20was%20a%20key%20talking%20point%20on%20result%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20defeated%20in%20its%20stronghold%20Gujarat%20in%20the%202027%20state%20polls.%20%26quot%3BTogether%20we%20are%20going%20to%20defeat%20them%20in%20Gujarat.%20We%20will%20defeat%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20in%20Gujarat%20just%20like%20we%20defeated%20them%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20be%20quite%20a%20task%20because%20in%20the%202022%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20state%2C%20winning%20156%20of%20the%20182%20Assembly%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20managed%20just%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20also%20drew%20the%20criticism%20of%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20BJP's%20ally%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ramvilas).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20remarks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20up%20of%20all%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20learn%20it%20is%20Faizabad%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20not%20Ayodhya.%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20constituency%20and%20is%20part%20of%20it.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20if%20they%20think%20Ayodhya's%20win%20is%20big%20for%20them%2C%20then%20we%20are%20also%20analysing%20our%20mistakes%20and%20working%20towards%20it.%20They%20couldn't%20even%20cross%20the%20mark%20of%2010