ops!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20mourn%20Viserys%20and%20the%20comparative%20peace%20of%20his%20era%20%E2%80%94%20but%20without%20his%20death%2C%20we%20really%20wouldn't%20have%20a%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9.%20Daemon%20murders%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20Lady%20Rhea%20Royce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rachel%20redford%20as%20lady%20rhea%20royce%20in%20house%20of%20the%20dragon%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20with%20brown%20hair%20pulled%20half%20back%2C%20wearing%20brown%20armor%20and%20sitting%20astride%20a%20white%20horse%2C%20riding%20through%20a%20grassland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668860881f0c1cd6d731f69a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Redford%20as%20Lady%20Rhea%20in%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20barely%20got%20to%20know%20Lady%20Rhea%20in%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20most%20of%20what%20we%20knew%20of%20her%20came%20from%20Daemon's%20mouth.%20Given%20that%20he%20referred%20to%20her%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BBronze%20Bitch%26quot%3B%20and%20refused%20to%20consummate%20their%20marriage%2C%20most%20of%20those%20words%20weren't%20very%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20meet%20her%20briefly%20in%20season%20one%2C%20episode%20five%2C%20shortly%20before%20Daemon%2C%20well%E2%80%A6%20murders%20her.%20Rhea%20seems%20independent%2C%20capable%2C%20and%20unafraid%20to%20taunt%20Daemon.%20That%20is%20until%20she%20clearly%20realizes%20that%20he's%20come%20to%20kill%20her%20and%20attempt%20to%20marry%20Rhaenrya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Rhea's%20death%20comes%20off%20more%20as%20a%20shock%2C%20given%20her%20little%20screentime%2C%20it's%20tragic%20to%20see%20her%20merely%20as%20a%20casualty%20of%20Daemon's%20ambition%20and%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3