use%20Helaena%20flees%20the%20room.%20But%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20brutality%20is%20displayed%20for%20all%20of%20King's%20Landing%20to%20see%20during%20Jaeharys'%20funeral%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20conflict%20between%20the%20greens%20and%20the%20blacks%2C%20an%20innocent%20child%20was%20slaughtered%20because%20of%20the%20squabble%20over%20the%20throne%2C%20and%20it's%20clear%20to%20everyone%20that%20the%20conflict%20has%20been%20taken%20beyond%20the%20point%20of%20no%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20Arryk%20and%20Erryk%20Cargyll%20killed%20each%20other%20after%20ending%20up%20on%20different%20sides%20of%20the%20war.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22House%20of%20the%20Dragon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885ca31f0c1cd6d731f5bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EErryk%20(Ellliot%20Tittensor)%20and%20Arryk%20(Luke%20Tittensor)%20Cargylle%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20Arryk%20Cargyll%20and%20Erryk%20Cargyll%20had%20more%20control%20over%20their%20deaths%2C%20since%20they%20chose%20to%20fight%20till%20the%20end%2C%20that%20doesn't%20make%20their%20deaths%20any%20less%20sad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20season%20one%2C%20the%20twins%20work%20together%20as%20Kingsguard%20protecting%20the%20royal%20family.%20But%20when%20the%20Greens%20usurp%20the%20throne%2C%20they%20are%20split%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Arryk%20sides%20with%20Aegon%20II%20while%20Erryk%20leaves%20and%20joins%20Rhaenyra's%20Queensguard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Criston%20Cole%20sends%20Arryk%20to%20slay%20Rhaenyra%20in%20episode%20two%2C%20the%20brothers'%20impending%20showdown%20begins.%20The%20scene%20is%20a%20messy%2C%20vicious%20fight%2C%20and%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20tell%20which%20twin%20wins.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20slaying%20his%20brother%2C%20Erryk%20stabs%20themselves%20with%20their%20sword%20after%20realizing%20what%20he%20has%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20heartbreaking%20that%20these%20twins%20are%20forced%20to%20pick%20duty%20over%20their%20own%20kin.%20Their%20deaths%20highlight%20how%20painful%20and%20destructive%20this%20civil%20war%20will%20be%20for%20the%20non-royal%20members%20of%20Westeros.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20Joffrey%20Lonmouth%20was%20brutally%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20Criston%20Cole.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20with%20shoulder-length%20hair%20stand%20side%20by%20side%20looking%20serious.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f27268f62ba18a7e1f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoffrey%20and%20Criston%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoffrey%20Lonmouth's%20death%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20we%20really%20saw%20Ser%20Criston%20Cole's%20true%20colors%2C%20and%20man%2C%20were%20they%20ugly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Rhaenyra%20and%20Laenor%20Velaryon%20were%20wed%2C%20they%20both%20had%20an%20understanding%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20pursue%20their%20other%20lovers%3A%20Criston%20and%20Joffrey.%20At%20their%20wedding%2C%20Joffrey%20confronts%20Criston.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20me%2C%20Ser%20Criston%2C%20but%20we%20are%20both%20deeply%20invested%20in%20this%20union%2C%26quot%3B%20Joffrey%20says.%20He%20tells%20Criston%20that%20Laenor%20is%20%26quot%3Bdear%26quot%3B%20to%20him%2C%20and%20that%20he%20understands%20Criston%20and%20Rhaenyra's%20relationship.%20It's%20a%20strategic%20move%20meant%20to%20unite%20them%20all%20in%20the%20shared%20secret%20of%20Laenor%20and%20Rhaenyra's%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that's%20not%20what%20happens.%20Instead%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20revelry%2C%20Criston%20brutally%20slays%20Joffrey%2C%20striking%20Laenor%20in%20the%20process.%20While%20we%20didn't%20know%20him%20particularly%20well%2C%20Joffrey%20didn't%20do%20anything%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20certainly%20nothing%20to%20merit%20Criston%20beating%20his%20face%20into%20a%20bloody%2C%20lifeless%20pulp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suddenness%2C%20brutality%2C%20and%20abject%20loss%20on%20Laenor's%20part%20of%20Joffrey's%20death%20merit%20its%20place%20on%20this%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20Laena%20Velaryon%20ordered%20Vhagar%20to%20kill%20her%20by%20fire.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20silvery%20curled%20hair%20and%20regal%20jewelry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885d24268f62ba18a7e173%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaena%20Velaryon%2C%20now%20married%20to%20Daemon%20Targaryen%2C%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20season%20features%20a%20second%20agonizing%20pregnancy-related%20death%2C%20as%20Laena%20Velaryon%20(Nanna%20Blondell)%20takes%20her%20own%20life%20in%20episode%20six.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20marrying%20Daemon%20and%20moving%20to%20Pentos%2C%20Laena%20struggles%20with%20a%20complicated%20birth%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20is%20offered%20the%20same%20choice%20that%20Viserys%20had%3A%20save%20his%20wife%2C%20or%20save%20the%20baby.%20However%2C%20Laena%20takes%20control%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20decides%20her%20own%20fate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20goes%20to%20her%20dragon%2C%20Vhagar%2C%20and%20commands%20him%20to%20burn%20her%20alive%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bdracarys%26quot%3B%20command.%20It's%20upsetting%20because%20Laena%20is%20forced%20into%20that%20situation%2C%20albeit%20at%20least%20it's%20her%20own%20decision.%20But%20seeing%20how%20reluctant%20Vhagar%20is%20to%20kill%20his%20rider%20just%20makes%20the%20whole%20scene%20even%20more%20upsetting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Rhaenys%20sacrifices%20herself%20and%20her%20dragon%2C%20Meleys%2C%20at%20Rook's%20Rest.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eve%20best%20and%20steve%20toussaint%20as%20rhaenys%20and%20corlys%20in%20house%20of%20the%20dragon%2C%20standing%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20council%20table.%20both%20are%20wearing%20black%20clothing%2C%20with%20their%20silver%20hair%20worn%20long%2C%20and%20rhaenys%20crosses%20her%20arms%20as%20she%20looks%20towards%20corlys%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885eb3268f62ba18a7e1d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEve%20Best%20and%20Steve%20Toussaint%20as%20Rhaenys%20and%20Corlys%20Velaryon%20in%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Rhaenys%20headed%20off%20to%20Rook's%20Rest%2C%20there%20was%20already%20a%20sense%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20three%2C%20she%20conversed%20with%20her%20husband%20about%20their%20legacy.%20Criston%20Cole%20and%20Aemond%20Targaryen%20clearly%20had%20a%20secret%20plan%20up%20their%20sleeves.%20There%20were%20too%20many%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20make%20her%20death%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Aemond%20and%20Vhagar%20any%20less%20tragic.%20Across%20the%20two%20seasons%2C%20Rhaenys%20has%20been%20brave%2C%20virtuous%2C%20loyal%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20badass%2C%20making%20her%20a%20favorite%20among%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20she%20realizes%20that%20she%20cannot%20defeat%20Vhagar%20at%20the%20battle%20of%20Rook's%20Rest%20in%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20four%2C%20she%20doesn't%20run%20away.%20Instead%2C%20she%20straps%20herself%20tighter%20in%20her%20seat%20and%20fights%20valiantly%20till%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20true%20noble%20warriors%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20gone%2C%20and%20to%20quote%20Otto%20Hightower%2C%20We%20(the%20audience%20and%20Westeros)%20%26quot%3Bare%20poorer%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20Queen%20Aemma%20dies%20during%20childbirth%20after%20Viserys%20orders%20his%20son%20to%20be%20cut%20out%20of%20her.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20with%20silver%20hair%20wearing%20medieval%20royalty%20garb%20stand%20lovingly%20next%20to%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885ee21f0c1cd6d731f633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaddy%20Considine%20and%20Sian%20Brooke%20costar%20as%20King%20Viserys%20and%20Queen%20Aemma%20in%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20made%20a%20bloody%20debut%20in%20the%20premiere%20episode%20of%20the%20first%20season%20with%20the%20heartbreaking%20death%20of%20King%20Viserys'%20(Paddy%20Considine)%20wife%2C%20Queen%20Aemma%20(Sian%20Brooke).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aemma%20goes%20into%20labor%2C%20the%20baby%20gets%20stuck%2C%20and%20Viserys%20is%20forced%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20save%20his%20wife%20or%20the%20baby.%20The%20King%20chooses%20his%20unborn%20child%20hoping%20to%20get%20a%20male%20heir%20to%20the%20Targaryen%20throne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20maesters%20cut%20Aemma's%20belly%20open%20to%20save%20the%20child%2C%20killing%20her%20in%20the%20process.%20It's%20tragic%20because%20Aemma's%20agency%20is%20taken%20away%20from%20her%2C%20and%20she's%20completely%20disregarded%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20male%20heir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20devastating%20scene%20is%20only%20made%20worse%20when%20the%20baby%2C%20Baelon%2C%20dies%20just%20one%20day%20after%20being%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Lucerys%20is%20the%20first%20major%20casualty%20of%20the%20Dance%20of%20the%20Dragons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rhaenyra%2C%20emma%20d'arcy%2C%20holding%20her%20sun%20lucerys%2C%20elliot%20grihault%2C%20in%20front%20of%20a%20strategy%20war%20table.%20she's%20looking%20at%20him%20intensely%2C%20and%20cracling%20his%20neck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f0b1aace5b3ada4d411%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElliot%20Grihault%20and%20Emma%20D'Arcy%20as%20Lucerys%20and%20Rhaenyra%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELucerys%20and%20his%20dragon%20Arrax's%20deaths%20are%20truly%20the%20biggest%20tragedies%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Greens%20and%20the%20Blacks%20were%20preparing%20for%20an%20eventual%20war%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20they%20could%20have%20found%20another%20way%20to%20settle%20the%20throne%20debate%20after%20a%20cooling-off%20period.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20reconciliation%20once%20Lucerys%2C%20a%20child%20and%20an%20heir%2C%20is%20slain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Lucerys'%20death%20essentially%20kick-start%20a%20terrible%20civil%20war%2C%20but%20it%20was%20entirely%20accidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20scene%20itself%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20horror%20movie%2C%20with%20Aemond%20and%20Vhagar%20stalking%20and%20taunting%20Lucerys%20and%20Arrax%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20rainy%20skies.%20Aemond%20sees%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20toy%20with%20and%20harm%20Lucerys%20as%20revenge%20for%20his%20eye%