0reshoots%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20small%20but%20impactful%20dialogue%20tweak%20courtesy%20of%20producer%20Sarah%20Hess%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%20send%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20it%20becomes%20an%20instruction%2C%20and%20it's%20then%20the%20final%20piece%20of%20guidance%20to%20Rhaenyra%2C%26quot%3B%20Best%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20she's%20doing%20is%20showing%20her%20how%20to%20be%20a%20good%20leader%20and%20how%20to%20rule%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20you%20do.%20You%20don't%20go%20in%20yourself%20because%20that's%20too%20risky%20for%20the%20bigger%20picture.%20You%20send%20in%20your%20best%20fighter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Rhaenys%20knows%20that%20she's%20crossing%20the%20point%20of%20no%20return%2C%20Best%20said.%20Though%20she's%20confident%20in%20volunteering%20herself%20and%20Meleys%2C%20she%20doesn't%20expect%20to%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20a%20sacrifice%2C%20because%20I%20feel%20that%20for%20Rhaenys%2C%20she's%20done%20everything%20to%20not%20have%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Best%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhoever%20crosses%20that%20line%20can't%20continue.%20There's%20no%20living%20after%20that.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20a%20sacrificial%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238bc03b3-dbcd-453f-b619-1dff1827163e%5C%22%3ERhaenys%20still%20exercises%20restraint%20during%20her%20final%20battle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERhaenys'%20actual%20death%20comes%20during%20a%20three-way%20dragon%20fight%20between%20Meleys%2C%20Vhagar%2C%20and%20Sunfyre.%20The%20emotional%20impact%20of%20that%20battle%20hinges%20on%20Best's%20performance.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-rhaenyra-lucerys-death-scene-director-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDirector%20Alan%20Taylor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20also%20directed%20the%20series%20premiere%2C%20doesn't%20hesitate%20to%20cut%20in%20close%20to%20her%20face%20as%20it%20becomes