ing%20the%20battle%2C%20Best%20says%20that%20Rhaenys%20is%20still%20reluctant%3A%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they're%20trying%20to%20kill%20her%2C%20Aegon%20and%20Aemond%20are%20still%20part%20of%20her%20family.%20During%20that%20sequence%2C%20Rhaenys%20is%20very%20specific%20in%20her%20commands%20to%20Meleys%3A%20she%20only%20orders%20the%20dragon%20to%20attack%20Sunfyre%20and%20Vhagar%2C%20even%20as%20her%20nephews%20commend%20%3Cem%3Edracarys%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20fire%20%E2%80%94%20with%20little%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20to%20me%20that%20every%20time%20anybody%20was%20on%20a%20dragon%20and%20was%20saying%20%3Cem%3Edracarys%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20human%20or%20person%20riding%20had%20reached%20a%20level%20of%20really%20high%20emotion%2C%20and%20it%20was%20very%20chaotic%2C%20and%20very%20vengeful%2C%20and%20very%20angry%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Best%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20important%20to%20me%20that%20she%20was%20different%20from%20all%20of%20those%20others%2C%20that%20she%20was%20an%20utter%20pro%20to%20the%20last%2C%20with%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThat%20grace%20characterizes%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frhaenys-death-house-of-the-dragon-eve-best-interview-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720404602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668842c11f0c1cd6d731ed8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frhaenys-death-house-of-the-dragon-eve-best-interview-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20sent%20Rhaenys%20and%20Meleys%20into%20battle.%20Eve%20Best%20broke%20down%20Rhaenys'%20death%20scene%2C%20and%20what%20dragon%20warfare%20really%20means%20in%20Westeros.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22phaasch%40busin