3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20before%20the%20how%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMays%20liked%20that%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20emphasized%20the%20impact%20he%20created.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20convince%20somebody%20that%20what%20I%20did%20was%20important%2C%20then%20they'll%20want%20to%20know%20how%20I%20did%20it.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20he%20added%20that%20his%20enhancements%20increased%20the%20speed%20of%20deployment%20by%2050%25.%20Then%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tell%20you%20how%20I%20did%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20that%20by%20using%20zip%20compression%20tools%20and%20algorithms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimplify%20jargon%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20technical%20jargon%20like%20names%20of%20software%2C%20Mays%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20assume%20that%20everyone%20reading%20his%20resume%20would%20know%20what%20some%20abbreviations%20mean.%20Just%20like%20formal%20writing%2C%20he%20uses%20the%20full%20names%20for%20each%20of%20those%20software%20on%20first%20mention%2C%20and%20use%20short%20forms%20after%20that.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20know%20your%20industry%20to%20know%20when%20it%20is%20appropriate%20to%20rely%20on%20an%20abbreviation%20versus%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5d2a4cc-f88a-4e9b-8e2f-de5b3259ee8f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20changes%20he%20would%20make%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20To%20better%20show%20impact%2C%20Mays%20would%20include%20more%20datapoints%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20a%20project%20to%20support%20a%20system%20for%20an%20e-commerce%20platform.%20For%20a%20big%20sales%20day%20like%20Black%20Friday%2C%20he%20would%20have%20highlighted%20how%20many%20thousands%20of%20people%20used%20the%20website%20per%20second%20to%20show%20the%20scale%20he%20was%20working%20at.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfessional%20summary%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mays%20said%20that%20his%202013%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20also%20lacked%20a%20professional%20summary.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is%20going%20to%20tell%20a%20story%2C%20and%20it's%20your%20job%20as%20the%20storyteller%20to%20make%20that%20narrative%20as%20easy%20to%20understand%20for%20someone%20who's%20only%20going%20to%20look%20at%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20maybe%20five%20seconds.%26quot%3B%20The%20summary%20should%20say%20why%20you're%20the%20perfect%20person%20for%20the%20role%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20his%20latest%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20Mays%20added%20three%20lines%20summarizing%20his%20roles%2C%20what%20he%20is%20passionate%20about%20and%20how%20he%20wants%20to%20add%20value%20to%20businesses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Mays%20recommends%20his%20clients%20follow%20a%20%26quot%3Br%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20formula%26quot%3B%20that%20looks%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20accomplished%20X%20as%20measured%20by%20Y%2C%20doing%20Z.%26quot%3B%20But%20for%20his%20own%20resume%2C%20he%20thinks%20he%20could%20have%20followed%20it%20better.%20For%20some%20of%20his%20bullet%20points%2C%20Mays%20talked%20about%20how%20he%20achieved%20something%2C%20but%20left%20out%20what%20impact%20his%20technology%20created%20on%20the%20company.%20%26quot%3BThe%20business%20context%20is%20missing%20from%20that%20bullet%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EMays%20worked%20at%20Google's%20Irvine%2C%20California%2C%20office%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20until%202022.%20He%20left%20to%20become%20an%20interview%20coach%20and%20public%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20or%20finance%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%20journey%3F%20Please%20get%20in%20touch%3A%20shubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-engineer-reviews-old-google-resume-pointers-keywords-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20I