%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2050%20farmers%20through%20online%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%20350%20grams%20of%20saffron%20of%20%E2%80%98mogra%E2%80%99%20variety%20in%20a%20tiny%20room.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1-1720186311-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%20350%20grams%20of%20saffron%20of%20%E2%80%98mogra%E2%80%99%20variety%20in%20a%20tiny%20room.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20shares%20a%20step-by-step%20guide%20for%20farmers%20willing%20to%20replicate%20the%20method%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Establish%20a%20controlled%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20saffron%20in%20warm%20Nandurbar%20village%20as%20he%20set%20up%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20this%2C%20I%20insulated%20the%20room%20to%20control%20the%20temperature.%20You%20can%20insulate%20the%20room%20using%20thermocol%20or%20puff%20panels%20if%20practising%20saffron%20in%20an%20open%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20also%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20proper%20machinery%20to%20ensure%20a%20similar%20climate%20like%20Kashmir.%20Install%20chillers%20from%20cold%20storages%20and%20humidifiers%20to%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20a%20temperature%20of%2015-20%20degrees%20should%20be%20maintained%20in%20September%20during%20the%20sprouting%20period%20and%205-7%20degrees%20from%20November%20to%20October%20at%20the%20time%20of%20flowering.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20provide%20direct%20harsh%20sunlight%20to%20saffron%2C%20so%20we%20used%20grow%20lights%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Procure%20bulbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20advises%20procuring%20saffron%20bulbs%20for%20sprouting%20only%20after%20preparing%20the%20unit.%20He%20sourced%20bulbs%20of%20%E2%80%98mogra%E2%80%99%20variety%20from%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20costs%20between%20Rs%20600%20and%20Rs%20800%20per%20kg.%20There%20are%20additional%20expenses%20for%20transportation.%20Farmers%20can%20start%20saffron%20cultivation%20from%20100%20kg%20of%20bulbs%20to%20get%20a%20yield%20of%20about%2030%20to%2040%20grams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20advises%20prefering%20plastic%20trays%20over%20wooden%20ones%20as%20it%20will%20be%20less%20prone%20to%20fungus%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-2-1720186406-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20advises%20preferring%20plastic%20trays%20over%20wooden%20ones%20as%20they%20will%20be%20less%20prone%20to%20fungus%20attacks.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Bulb%20treatment%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20saffron%20bulbs%20are%20prone%20to%20fungus%20attacks%20and%20require%20special%20care%20during%20transportation.%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20sort%20the%20bulbs%20as%20per%20their%20size%20and%20remove%20dirt%20and%20mud.%20Thereafter%2C%20dip%20them%20in%20neem%20oil%20solution%20to%20remove%20bacteria.%20Dry%20them%20naturally%20inside%20the%20room%20under%20the%20fan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlace%20these%20bulbs%20on%20trays%20for%20sprouting.%20Prefer%20plastic%20trays%20over%20wooden%20ones%20as%20it%20will%20be%20less%20prone%20to%20fungus%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Maintenance%20of%20temperature%20and%20sanitisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20uses%20the%20aeroponics%20technique%20where%20bulbs%20are%20grown%20in%20soilless%20media%20and%20nutrients%20are%20supplied%20through%20air.%20In%20this%20setup%2C%20he%20has%20also%20installed%20humidifiers%20and%20air%20conditioners%20to%20provide%20a%20proper%20climate%20for%20saffron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%2015%C3%9715%2C%20I%20installed%20air%20conditioners%20that%20automatically%20regulate%20temperature.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20the%20desired%20temperature%20is%20attained%20then%20it%20automatically%20switches%20off%2C%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20temperature%20reduces%20by%20three%20degrees%2C%20it%20restarts.%20The%20power%20expenses%20amount%20to%20around%20Rs%206%2C000%20to%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20month.%20We%20can%20harness%20solar%20energy%20as%20well%20to%20reduce%20power%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20saffron%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20easy%20provided%20proper%20temperature%20and%20cleanliness%20are%20ensured.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20and%20humidity%2C%20which%20varies%20from%20sowing%20to%20the%20flowering%20stage.%20Maintain%20humidity%20between%2060%20and%2070%20percent%20in%20the%20unit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warns%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20let%20anyone%20enter%20the%20unit%2C%20and%20if%20necessary%2C%20wear%20masks%20and%20apply%20sanitisers%20so%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20risk%20of%20diseases%20affecting%20the%20bulbs.%20However%2C%20in%20case%20of%20fungus%20attack%2C%20remove%20the%20affected%20bulbs%20from%20others%20and%20treat%20them%20with%20neem%20oil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Harvest%20stigma%20sticks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20farmers%20can%20harvest%20saffron%20once%20a%20year%20as%20saffron%20has%20a%20life%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20dormancy%2C%20flowering%2C%20and%20multiplication%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CSaffron%20is%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20late%20October.%20You%20can%20pluck%20stigma%20sticks%20(flower%E2%80%99s%20thread-like%20structures)%20from%20saffron%20crocus.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20get%20three%20stigma%20sticks%20from%20each%20flower.%20Place%20them%20on%20a%20clean%20cloth%20and%20dry%20them%20naturally%20under%20the%20fan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20adds%20that%20farmers%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20gram%20by%20selling%20saffron%20stigma%20sticks.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20easier%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20market%20and%20earn%20handsomely.%20Currently%2C%20the%20market%20is%20dominated%20by%20cheap%20imports%20from%20Iran.%20You%20can%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20by%20selling%20authentic%20red%20saffron%2C%20which%20does%20not%20dissolve%20in%20water%20and%20leaves%20a%20shiny%20golden%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20harvesting%20comes%20the%20multiplication%20stage%20of%20daughter%20corms.%20This%20process%20requires%20soil%20and%20cocopeat%20media.%20It%20takes%20up%20to%20four%20months%20for%20the%20process%2C%20wherein%20a%20bulb%20gets%20multiplied%20into%20two.%20These%20bulbs%20can%20be%20saved%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720188130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1720186205.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harsh%20Patil%2C%20from%20Nandurbar%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20turned%20to%20innovative%20farming%20techniques%20after%20climate%20change%20affected%20his%20family's%20traditional%20crops.%20He%20started%20growing%20saffron%20using%20aeroponics%20in%20a%20small%20room%2C%20earning%20lakhs.%20He%20shares%20a%20step-by-step%20guide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355809%2Fgrow-saffron-indoors-aeroponics-steps-guide-harsh-patil-nandurbar-maharashtra-earn-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Go%20Home%2C%20This%20Job%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20for%20You%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20I%20Built%20a%20Career%20in%20the%20Male-Dominated%20Merchant%20Navy%22%2C%22cont