astic%20waste%20in%202014%20when%20the%20Swachhata%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20was%20launched.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20inspired%20by%20my%20mother.%20Back%20in%20the%2060s%2C%20she%20used%20to%20wear%20polyester%20sarees.%20She%20would%20burn%20worn-out%20sarees.%20When%20polyester%20burns%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20plasticy%20smell%20and%20the%20fabric%20melts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20would%20mix%20the%20molten%20fabric%20with%20ash%20from%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20make%20a%20thick%20paste.%20She%20would%20apply%20the%20semi-solid%20substance%20onto%20a%20bamboo%20%3Cem%3Esoop%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20tray)%20to%20make%20it%20rigid.%20This%20would%20increase%20its%20durability%20from%20a%20year%20to%20four%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20she%20started%20using%20it%20to%20fix%20broken%20pans%20and%20drums.%20She%20never%20went%20to%20school%20but%20I%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20ways%20of%20reusing%20plastic%20remained%20with%20Dr%20Balmukund.%20He%20utilised%20this%20concept%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143206%2Fhyderabad-office-recycled-plastic-waste-bamboo-bamboo-house-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20house%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhen%20IAS%20Vivek%20Johnson%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20Zila%20Parishad%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20was%20constructed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Zila%20Parishad%20Chandrapur.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia