ds%2C%20providing%20them%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20stay%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%20empowering%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20skill%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafety%2C%20education%20and%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveksha%20team%20first%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20children%20of%20the%20migrant%20labourers%20to%20understand%20the%20major%20gaps.%20They%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20facility%20for%20these%20children%20to%20spend%20time%20during%20the%20day%20and%20they%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20gain%20admission%20in%20government%20schools%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20identification%20documents%20like%20an%20Aadhar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-500x336.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-768x517.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-150x101.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffig